    "client_msg_id": "d4d4c0b8-b781-4bcd-b44c-229ae5cd796d",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "<@UFPPABQ7P> it's been running for &gt;=6 months with a couple hundred users without any unplanned downtime for users. planned downtime was only 1 DB upgrade in the period. however it seems like you'd need a dashdash API. we currently let you interact with APIs from dashdash, the reverse is still WIP.",
